study_design_info.intervention_model_description:
A parallel design model with 2 treatment arms:
NaF varnish: Application of a 5% NaF varnish (Duraphat, Colgate-Palmolive Ltd, Waltrop, Germany) on the occlusal surfaces of primary second molars and all other teeth, every 3 months during the study period;
GI sealant: Glass ionomer sealant (GC Fuji VII速 (pink)) on all primary second molars included in the studies, with no further repair/replacement of the sealant
